
== Depends ==

ant, GNU gettext

== To compile on Linux ==

$ export CLASSPATH="/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun/jre/lib/:.:/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun/jre/:/usr/lib/jvm/java-6-sun/jre/lib/plugin.jar"
$ ant

== To generate new .pot file ==

 * Generate .pot file
   xgettext -k_ -o po/messages.pot src/Translatable.java

 * Merge an existing .po file with a new .pot file
   msgmerge -U po/de/messages.po po/messages.pot

